// src/pages/about.astro
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Jay Kinkade</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Jay Kinkade - Melbourne dad, former poker player, now building things on the internet.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="nav-logo">JK</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="bio">
                <p>I spent twenty years playing poker and daily fantasy sports at a high level.</p>
                <p>That world gave me a front-row seat to people navigating psychology, risk, and decision-making under pressure.</p> 
                <p>These days, I've shifted my focus towards creating digital products.</p> 
                <p>I'm still fascinated by why people click what they click; I've just moved from competitively clicking buttons to designing the buttons myself.</p>
                <p>When I'm not working, I'm wrangling two small kids, keeping 30 houseplants alive, and figuring out DIY projects I probably should have hired someone for.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100%;
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        color: #2c2825;
        background: #faf9f7;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        height: 100vh;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1rem 4rem;
        max-width: calc(850px + 8rem);
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-logo {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #a08060;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        color: #857c72;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.813rem;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a.active {
        color: #2c2825;
    }

    .main {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 2rem 4rem;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 550px;
    }

    .bio p {
        font-size: 0.938rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #857c72;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .bio p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .bio a {
        color: #a08060;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .bio a:hover {
        color: #2c2825;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body {
            height: auto;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: auto;
        }

        .nav {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .main {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .bio p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
    }
</style>
